description.en:
Velleman VTHD09 precision drill bit/engraver set

Do you like to do a little DIY at home? Then this set is ideal for you. With the drill and engraver set you can make the most beautiful creations!

Specifications:
Colour: grey, multicoloured
Gender: unisex, junior
Material: plastic, steel
Capacity of the mandrel: 3.2 mm max
Speed: 10000-32000 rpm / with speed control
Power supply: 220-240 VAC 50 Hz
Consumption: 135 W
